note.p: Burial : The Lady Chapel, Wells Cathedral
Education: Westminster School; Christ Church College, Oxford. BA (1805), MA (1807), BD (1819), DD (1820)
Career: Headmaster, Westminster School (1819); Prebendary of York (1824); Prebendary of Carlisle (1826); Prebendary of Westminster (1827); Dean of Wells (1831)
Notes: John Caley has signed election certificate twice
